Yes, but not - not much. In fact I think - that was about the only occasion really that I think that I had a good thrashing. I would get a - what my - my mother would call a clout. You know, sort of - smack across the - ears or something
 like that. Which didn't hurt anybody. And incidentally if a policeman could do that, were enabled to do that today we should be much better.
